The paper deals with privacy concerns related to smart meters, which is a topic that falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also considers the use of renewable energy and a storage device, which involves control systems (cs.SY) and information theory (cs.IT). Additionally, the paper involves cyber-physical systems (cs.CY) and probability and statistics (cs.PF) in its analysis of the information leakage rate.
